  "whatsapp_greeting": "\ud83d\udc4b Welcome to *TouchNet Support*!\n\nI'm your AI assistant and I can help you:\n\u2022 \ud83c\udfab *Raise a support ticket* \u2014 just describe your issue\n\u2022 \ud83d\udd0d *Track an existing ticket* \u2014 send your ticket number (e.g. TKT-123456)\n\u2022 \ud83d\udcb3 *Check your account* \u2014 ask about invoices or your service plan\n\u2022 \ud83c\udf10 *Troubleshoot issues* \u2014 connectivity, speed, WiFi problems\n\nPlease describe how I can help you today, or share your *email address* so I can pull up your account.",
